                Frontend designing

1)create a project - ng new e-commerce
2)Run Anguler - ng serve -o
3)Add Bootstap,Fontawesome,GoogleFont
4)Lazy Loading-
    -Its a process of a loading components and modules
    -It improves application load time and performance

    ->ng g m products --route products --module app.module

5)Add<router-outlet></router-outlet> selector into the route component -app.component.html

6)create a component should lazy loaded in the prodect module
    ->all products -  ng g c products/all-products
    ->cart- ng g c products/cart
    ->wishlist - ng g c products/wishlist

7)Setup path for each module
    ->product-routing module

8)PageNotFound-ng g c page-not-found - 

9)Create Header and footer
    ->ng g c header
    ->ng g c footer
10)Designing of FrontEnd

11)Integration
    a)creating services for API calling
        - ng g s products/api
    b)import HttpClientModule in product module
    c)Dependency injection HttpClient class in API
12)Page Designing
13)Search for a product
    ng g p products/pipes/filter
